quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  4,38,"and those who spend their wealths for show in front of people and believe neither in Allah nor in the Last Day. And whoever has Satan as a comrade, then how evil is such a comrade!"
  4,39,"And what harm would it have done them, had they believed in Allah and the Last Day and spent out of what Allah had provided them? And Allah has always been All-Knowing about them."
  4,40,"Indeed, Allah does not do an atom’s weight of injustice. And if <span class=""h"">it is a good<sup foot_note=""79853"" class=""qiraat"">1</sup> </span><span class=""h"">deed</span>, He multiplies it and gives from Himself a great reward."
  4,41,"So how will it be when We bring forth a witness from every community and We bring you<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>forth as a witness over all these?"
  4,42,"On that day, those who denied and disobeyed the Messenger wish that the earth would be leveled with them, for they conceal nothing from Allah."
  4,43,"O you who have attained faith, do not approach prayer while you are drunk so that you may know what you say, nor while you are in a state of major impurity{1}—unless you are traveling—until you have bathed. And if you are sick or traveling or one of you returns from relieving oneself or you have touched women<i class=""s"">(in intercourse) </i>and cannot find water, then find clean soil and wipe your faces and your hands with it. Indeed, Allah has always been Pardoning, Oft-Forgiving.",footnotes:1:A state of major impurity after sexual discharge, requiring a full body wash.
  4,44,"Have you<a class=""sup""><sup>sg </sup></a>not seen those who were given a share of the Scripture? They purchase utter misguidance and want you<a class=""sup""><sup>pl </sup></a>to stray from the way."
